summary:
* masseur 
* writer and editor

During my travels in Asia I have explored several spiritual practices and healing modalities, most notably yoga and Ayurvedic massage. I specialise in Indian deep-tissue massage, a powerful tool to free the body of tension and remove blockages. It may also help to improve postural structure and movement dynamics, and increases overall well-being.
